title: UDO - 1997 - Solid [320kbs] ~~Renovatio~~
description:
Solid is U.D.O.'s fifth album. Since the last album, Udo Dirkschneider had been busy with his old band Accept's reunion, which resulted in three albums.

Accept's drummer Stefan Kaufmann entered U.D.O. as guitar player on this album.

The album was recorded and mixed at ROXX Studios,
